narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Yes - all information was made available in a timely manner. Again, Bryan's extensive lecture notes were an unbelievable resource.
The BAC drawing room is a great resource throughout the semester. Seeing landscape painting and drawings in person made a huge difference for me.
The holdings at the Center for British Arts are unmatched.
